---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import lr from '@/images/lr.jpg';
import tl from '@/images/tl.jpg';
import el from '@/images/el.jpg';
import dy from '@/images/dy.jpg';
import pp from '@/images/pp.png';
import pfp from '@/images/pfp.webp';
---
<section class=" bg-white ">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-8 pb-16">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-carrot font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl px-8 pb-4">
        Team leader
      </h2>
      <div class="text-black text-xs flex flex-col mx-auto px-8 pt-2">
        <ul class="space-y-16">
          <li class="bg-gray-100 p-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4">
              <div class="hidden md:flex-shrink-0 md:block w-32 h-40">
                <Image src={lr} alt="Liss Vázquez Rodríguez" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                <h3 class="text-black font-display text-xl md:text-2xl mb-2">Dr. Liss Vázquez Rodríguez</h3>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.mpi-hd.mpg.de/mpi/en/" class="text-carrot hover:underline text-sm md:text-base">
                  MPIK, P.I LIAF Group
                </a>
                <ul class="pt-4 space-y-1">
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-700">EP-Dept./ISOLDE, 1211 Geneva 23, Switzerland</li>
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base">+41 22 767 2783</li>
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base">
                    <a href="mailto:liss.vazquez.rodriguez@cern.ch" class="text-carrot hover:underline">liss.vazquez.rodriguez@cern.ch</a>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>                                                   
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base mt-3">
              Dr. Liss Vázquez Rodríguez is a prominent physicist specializing in experimental nuclear physics. She is affiliated with the Max-Planck-Institut für Kernphysik (MPIK) in Heidelberg, Germany, and is actively involved in research at CERN, particularly within the ISOLDE facility. Her work focuses on high-resolution laser spectroscopy, a technique used to study the properties of atomic nuclei, especially those that are neutron-rich or otherwise challenging to examine. 
              Dr. Rodríguez has made significant contributions to understanding nuclear structure and dynamics, particularly through her work on isotopes of elements like tellurium and antimony. She is also a key member of the COLLAPS collaboration at CERN, which explores nuclear charge radii and electromagnetic moments among other nuclear characteristics. <a target="_blank" href="https://www.mpi-hd.mpg.de/mpi/en/research/scientific-divisions-and-groups/stored-and-cooled-ions/members/liss-v-rodriguez" class="text-carrot hover:underline">More...</a>
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-carrot font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl px-8 pb-4">
        Project Associate
      </h2>
      <div class="text-black text-xs flex flex-col mx-auto px-8 pt-2">
        <ul class="space-y-16">
          <li class="bg-gray-100 p-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4">
              <div class="hidden md:flex-shrink-0 md:block w-32 h-40">
                <Image src={dy} alt="Liss Vázquez Rodríguez" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                <h3 class="text-black font-display text-xl md:text-2xl mb-2">Dr. Deyan Yordanov</h3>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.mpi-hd.mpg.de/mpi/en/" class="text-carrot hover:underline text-sm md:text-base">
                  MPIK, LIAF Group
                </a>
                <ul class="pt-4 space-y-1">
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-700">EP-Dept./ISOLDE, 1211 Geneva 23, Switzerland</li>
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base">+33 169 153 307</li>
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base "><a href="mailto:lyordanov@ipno.in2p3.fr" class="text-carrot hover:underline">yordanov@ipno.in2p3.fr</a></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>                                                   
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base mt-3">
              Dr. Deyan Yordanov is a researcher and academic associated with Université Paris-Sud, now part of Université Paris-Saclay, one of the leading research universities in France. Université Paris-Saclay is known for its excellence in science and engineering, and it collaborates with several prestigious institutions and research centers.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-carrot font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl px-8 pb-4">
        Postdocs
      </h2>
      <div class="text-black text-xs flex flex-col mx-auto px-8 pt-2">
        <ul class="space-y-16">
          <li class="bg-gray-100 p-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4">
