              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                <h3 class="text-black font-display text-xl md:text-2xl mb-2">Dr. Peter Plattner</h3>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://home.cern/" class="text-carrot hover:underline text-sm md:text-base">
                  CERN research fellow
                </a>
                <ul class="pt-4 space-y-1">
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-700">EP-Dept./ISOLDE, 1211 Geneva 23, Switzerland</li>
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base">+43 650 4034 208</li>
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base">
                    <a href="mailto:peter.plattner@cern.ch" class="text-carrot hover:underline">peter.plattner@cern.ch</a>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>                                                   
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base mt-3">
              Dr. Peter Plattner is a researcher involved in experimental atomic and nuclear physics, particularly in the field of laser spectroscopy. He is affiliated with the Max Planck Institute for Nuclear Physics in Heidelberg and contributes to the COLLAPS experiment at CERN's ISOLDE facility. This experiment focuses on collinear laser spectroscopy to study exotic nuclei.
              M.Sc. Tim Lellinger works alongside Dr. Plattner on the COLLAPS project. However, there is no information available on an individual named Edward Ilattheus within this context or similar research areas. <a target="_blank" href="https://miracls.web.cern.ch/CVs/cv_peter.pdf" class="text-carrot hover:underline">More...</a>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="bg-gray-100 p-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4">
              <div class="hidden md:flex-shrink-0 md:block w-32 h-40">
                <Image src={tl} alt="Liss Vázquez Rodríguez" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                <h3 class="text-black font-display text-xl md:text-2xl mb-2">Tim Lellinger</h3>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://home.cern/" class="text-carrot hover:underline text-sm md:text-base">
                  LIAF Group
                </a>
                <ul class="pt-4 space-y-1">
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-700">EP-Dept./ISOLDE, 1211 Geneva 23, Switzerland</li>
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base">+41 22 767 2783</li>
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base">
                    <a href="mailto:tim.enrico.lellinger@cern.ch" class="text-carrot hover:underline">tim.enrico.lellinger@cern.ch</a>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>                                                   
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base mt-3">
              Tim Enrico Lellinger is a Ph.D. student and researcher affiliated with ISOLDE at CERN and the Institute for Nuclear Physics at TU Darmstadt. His work is primarily focused on experimental nuclear physics, where he is involved in research related to laser spectroscopy, particularly through the LaserSpHERe group.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-carrot font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl px-8 pb-4">
        PhD Students
