          <li class="bg-gray-100 p-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4">
              <div class="hidden md:flex-shrink-0 md:block w-32 h-40">
                <Image src={pfp} alt="Liss Vázquez Rodríguez" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                <h3 class="text-black font-display text-xl md:text-2xl mb-2">Ronaldo Menendez</h3>
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.mpi-hd.mpg.de/mpi/en/" class="text-carrot hover:underline text-sm md:text-base">
                  MPIK, LIAF Group
                </a>
                <ul class="pt-4 space-y-1">
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-700">-</li>
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base">-</li>
                  <li class="text-sm md:text-base "><a href="mailto:jbh@ns.ph.liv.ac.uk" class="text-carrot hover:underline">-</a></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>                                                   
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base mt-3">
              A researcher associated with the Max Planck Institute for Nuclear Physics (MPIK) in Heidelberg, Germany. He works within the Cosmic Ray Research Division at MPIK, which focuses on high-energy cosmic rays and gamma-ray astronomy.          </li>
        </ul>
